import React, { useState, useEffect } from 'react'; import { Link } from 'react-router-dom'; import { useAuth } from '../context/AuthContext'; import api from '../utils/api'; const Dashboard = () => { const { user } = useAuth(); const [stats, setStats] = useState({ totalRestaurants: 0, }); const [loading, setLoading] = useState(true); useEffect(() => { fetchStats(); }, []); const fetchStats = async () => { try { const [restaurantsRes, contactsRes] = await Promise.all([ api.get('/restaurants'), api.get('/contact') ]); const restaurants = restaurantsRes.data.restaurants || []; const contacts = contactsRes.data.contacts || []; setStats({ totalRestaurants: restaurants.length, activeRestaurants: restaurants.filter(r => r.status === 'active').length, totalContacts: contacts.length, }); } catch (error) { console.error('Error fetching stats:', error); } finally { setLoading(false); } }; if (loading) { return (
